
1  

Kosodi kanen, nakelimokiniata Sanabalat ka Tobia, ka Gesem Earabut, ka lukasurupokosi ice, ebe abu eoŋ kaduk arwatat, komamei arorwa nakesalakinit tomake (karaida keriŋa eoŋ esipokina ikirigin lukorutei kapaarasia kaŋun); 
2  

Keyakikis Sanabalat ka Gesem eoŋ kobalas ebe, “Kobia, keriamunos ediopet koreria luka apuuton naka Ono.” Konye keomito aiswamakin eoŋ aronis. 
3  

Kasodi aijukar ikiyakia mama ejaas kesi ebe, “Eswamai eoŋ aswam naepol, mam apedori alosit: inyo bo ti kitaŋania aswam, eoŋ ajalakin ŋes abunore mama ijaas?” 
4  

Keyakikis bobo kwaŋin irwan aoŋon; kaboŋok kwape kwaŋin. 
5  Kosodi Sanabalat aijukun ekekejaanakinan kwape kwaŋin irwan nakikanyet kitiŋite ebalua loepukoro kakanike; 
6  

ewadikatai kotomake ebe, “Elimorokinitai toma atekerin, abu da Gasimu kolim ebe, kwape iwomitotor ijo ka Iyudayan aipaliikin; ŋes kiinakini iduki arwatat: ikoto araun ekabakakec, kwape ejaatar akiro ŋun. 
7  Ibwaiki da inabin luelimonokinete nukon ko Yerusalem, kineras atiar, ‘Ejai ekabaka toma Yuda’: kwana da itejenunio ekabaka kwape ejaatar akiro ŋun. Aso do, kobia, kenerut.” 
8  

Kasodi aiyakikin ŋes ebe, “Mam iswamaunitai akiro ŋun kwape inerar ijo, konye isabi ijo elopet kotaukon.” 
9  

Naarai akotosi kesi kere aitukurian sio ebe, “Kokalanyakata akaninikec, kinyek aswam aiswamaunio.” Konye kwana, wu Edeke, kitogogoŋ ijo akakanin.


10  

Abu kalot togo loka Semaia okoku loka Delaia okoku loka Meketabel, loagolokinitoi; kotema ŋesi atiar, “Keriamakinos oni togo loka Edeke, toma oyekalu; ido kagolokis ikekia luka eyekalu: naarai epote aiar jo; eebo, epote aiar jo kuare.” 
11  

Katema atiar, “Etuŋanan loetia ne bala eoŋ tikeker? Iŋai da loetia ne bala eoŋ yeni ti keloma oyekalu aitajar akeijar? Mam alomari.” 
12  

Kamisiik, ido koany, mam abu Edeke kijukunite ŋes: konye abu ŋesi kolimite adwaretait na nakaluikin: naarai aropitos Tobia ka Sanabalat ŋes. 
13  Keropio kakirot kana tetere akurianari eoŋ kasodi aswam ŋun, kadiaka, kosodete kesi adumun akirot naerono kasodete amoromoroo. 
14  

Wu Ekadeke, kiitu Tobia ka Sanabalat kwape ajaatar aswamisiokec nu, ka anabi Noadia da, ka inabin ice, luti ketukurianata.


15  Kodaun arwatat kapaaran naka akaisaarei ka nukany kolap Elul, kotoma apaarasia akaisakany ka nuarei. 
16  

Kosodi kanen, kepuputu lukasurupokosi ŋun, kokuriakaros ikapirin kere lukirimorito sio, kodisiakaros kesi kakonyenekec: naarai koanyutu ebe aswam na eswamaa Edekekosi. 
17  Ido kapaarasia kaŋun apotu isotia luka Yuda kiyakiasi ibaluan luipu mama ejai Tobia, luka Tobia da kopotu mama ajaas kesi. 
18  Naarai ajaas koYuda luipu luapotu kiyapoikinito naarai kerai ŋesi ekamuran loka Sekania okoku loka Ara; abu okokuke Yekokanan komanyite akoku naka Mesulam okoku loka Berekia. 
19  Ido kinerenenas aswamisioke nuejok kakonyeneka, kolimonokinete ŋes akiroka. Kiyakuununei Tobia ibaluan aisiyonia eoŋ.

